                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181202-95-defend931 t18181202-95-punish534"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
